---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy | LearnEnglish.Life" description="Learn how LearnEnglish.Life collects, uses, and protects your personal information.">
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-emerald-700 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-emerald-100 text-lg">
        Last updated: April 5, 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          LearnEnglish.Life is operated entirely by AI systems. We collect minimal information necessary to provide our service:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> We use Google Analytics 4 to understand how visitors use our site. This includes pages visited, time spent, and general geographic location (city level only).</li>
          <li><strong>Email Subscriptions:</strong> If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address. You can unsubscribe at any time.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use essential cookies for site functionality and analytics cookies (with consent) to improve our service.</li>
          <li><strong>User-Submitted Content:</strong> Any reviews, comments, or feedback you submit becomes publicly visible content.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>To deliver our newsletter and service updates (only if subscribed)</li>
          <li>To analyze and improve our website and content</li>
          <li>To display relevant advertisements through Google AdSense</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          We use trusted third-party services:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Google Analytics 4:</strong> For website analytics. You can opt out using browser extensions.</li>
          <li><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> For advertising. Google's privacy policy applies to ads served by AdSense.</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> For CDN and security. Their privacy policy applies.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">4. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          We use the following types of cookies:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for site functionality (language preference, cookie consent)</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Help us understand how you use our site (with your consent)</li>
          <li><strong>Advertising Cookies:</strong> Used by Google AdSense to show relevant advertisements</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          We retain your email address until you unsubscribe. Analytics data is retained for 26 months. User-submitted reviews and comments are retained indefinitely as they become part of our public content.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Depending on your location, you may have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your personal data</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
          <li>Object to certain processing of your data</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          To exercise these rights, email us at privacy@learnenglish.life.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">7. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Our site is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">9. International Transfers</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Your information may be transferred and processed in countries outside your own. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. The "Last updated" date will reflect the most recent changes.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">11. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:<br>
          <strong>Email:</strong> privacy@learnenglish.life<br>
          <strong>Address:</strong> LearnEnglish.Life (AI-Operated)
        </p>

        <div class="bg-neutral-800 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-100 mb-2">AI Transparency Notice</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
            LearnEnglish.Life is operated entirely by artificial intelligence systems. This privacy policy was created by our AI team. For questions or requests, email privacy@learnenglish.life.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Base>
